body.text: "ChatLabs has been a reliable partner for us from day one. Not only did they have the kind of China solutions we needed, but also the strategies, working with us to make sure we were truly engaging our customers. We feel that we have a true partner that is supporting our goals and keeping us in the know in China’s ever-evolving digital ecosystem. "

content.text: Explore how we are helping brands in your industry find success.
Bringing brand stories to life and engaging with consumers on an individual basis.
Achieving the highest levels of security and compliance while serving clients.
Carefully crafted  personalized content at the right time during the guest experience.
Customer-centric experiences for China powered by a compliance-first data solution.
Collect rich data on your WeChat followers, create segments based on social behaviors, and engage consumers with personalized content and experiences.
Create a beautiful, rich brand experience and engaging product exploration. Optimize conversion by tracking behaviors and using AI recommendations.
Nurture leads from stores and the direct social network of your sales associates. Track interests, interactions, and serve existing clients to grow lifetime customer value.
Ensure data residency and compliance with China’s data protection laws. Get local-only storage and processing of regulated data while delivering data to any enterprise application.
Get to know our Guangzhou office.
VP of Operations
A part of ChatLabs since time immemorial. Down-to-earth vibes, carpe diem lifestyle, but we call him “The Boss.”
Sr Marketing Manager
Always up to something: playing sports, learning languages, going on bike rides, being an occasional couch potato, and, of course, planning events.
Senior Account Manager
A passionate storyteller, nature lover, and Chelsea football club fan. He loves to explore different cultures and watch Chelsea beating other football teams.
Accountant
When not crunching the numbers, she’s crunching on office snacks. The best “numbers person” you could ask for.
Test Engineer
Never passes up a good barbecue or basketball game. As our test engineer, he's known as “The One with the Most Answers.”
Front-End Developer
Enjoys singing (even though she thinks she’s a bit tone-deaf) and has a passion for food, puzzles, and arts & crafts. Always looking for opportunities to laugh and have fun.
认识一下我们的“搬砖工”
运营副总裁
自古以来就是ChatLabs的一份子。脚踏实地的性格配上及时行乐生活方式，加上豪爽霸气的特质使我们称他为“大佬”。
高级市场营销经理
总是在忙着玩飞盘，骑自行车，学习语言，偶尔做一个宅女，当然还有策划活动。
高级客户经理
热爱讲故事，热爱自然，是切尔西足球俱乐部的球迷。他喜欢花时间了解不同的人和文化，探索世界。
前端开发者
喜欢觅食、拼图、做手工和唱歌(尽管她认为自己有点五音不全)。总是在寻找大笑和娱乐的机会。
